## FAQs

**How do I scan a bottle?**  
Open the app, tap Scan, and point your camera at the bottle label.

**Can I edit or delete entries?**  
Yes. Any drink you add can be edited or removed at any time.

**Is my data backed up?**  
All data is stored locally on your device. If you remove the app, your data will be removed as well.
